// Modelo 111 — IRPF withholdings practiced on payments to workers, professionals,
// agrarian activities, etc. Each row represents a withholding event at the moment
// of payment (gross-up of cuenta 4751 H.P. acreedor por retenciones practicadas).
// Aggregated by quarter to produce AEAT Modelo 111.
model WithholdingTaxRecord {
  id               String    @id @default(cuid())
  organizationId   String    @map("organization_id")
